data.title: Secretariat: ACE
data.text:
The ACE General Secretariat informs the Executive Board and Member Organisations of all important questions arising from the policies and actions undertaken by the European Union, that are likely to impact the architectural profession. It assists the Executive Board in its mission and is moreover in charge of supervising the emergence and transparence of the decisions taken by the organisation, thus ensuring the continuity of the organisation.

The ACE Secretariat has its office in Brussels.

To contact our team, please send an e-mail at info(at)ace-cae(dot)eu.
